        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>Help patients manage their healthcare appointments. This includes booking new appointments with a selected doctor, viewing upcoming appointments, cancelling a scheduled appointment, and rescheduling an appointment to a new date and time.
Do not access or modify past or completed appointments. Do not provide medical advice or clinical guidance. If a request cannot be completed, offer to connect the patient to support.</scope>
