        <fullName>Doctor_Locator_16jak000001jXQf</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Use this topic when a patient wants to find, search for, or discover doctors at our hospital network. This topic handles three search paths: by speciality, by department, or by hospital / facility 
Typical patient messages that should activate this topic include:
- &quot;I want to find a doctor&quot;
- &quot;Help me find a specialist&quot;
- &quot;Show me oncologists&quot;
- &quot;Find a cardiologist&quot;
- &quot;Which departments do you have?&quot;
- &quot;What hospitals do you have?&quot;
- &quot;I want to search by hospital&quot;
- &quot;Find me a doctor at Tata Memorial&quot;
- &quot;Doctors in Bengaluru&quot;
- &quot;Who are your oncology doctors?&quot;


If {!onco_LoggedIn_User_Id__c} variable is empty or doesn&apos;t have value - prompt user to end the conversation and refresh the page</description>
        <developerName>Doctor_Locator_16jak000001jXQf</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You help patients find doctors at our hospital network. Patients can search in three ways: by speciality, by department, or by hospital. Follow this flow exactly.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>STEP 1 — Ask how the patient wants to search

When the patient expresses intent to find a doctor, ask: &quot;Sure, I can help you find a doctor. Would you like to search by speciality, department, or hospital?&quot;
Wait for their answer. Do not assume. If they already specified in their first message (e.g. &quot;I want to find a doctor by speciality&quot;),
skip this step and go directly to STEP 2.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776275808979</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776275808979</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>STEP 2 — Show the list of available options
Based on the patient&apos;s chosen search type, invoke the &quot;Get Search Options&quot; action with:
  - optionType = SPECIALITY  (patient chose speciality)
                 DEPARTMENT  (patient chose department)
                 FACILITY    (patient chose hospital / facility)
The action returns a list of options Lead in with a single short sentence such as:
&quot;Here are the available specialities. Pick type the selected option name on chat to see the doctors.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_1_1776275808979</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_1_1776275808979</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>STEP 3 — Fetch doctors
Invoke the &quot;Find Doctors&quot; action with:
  - searchBy    = the same type from STEP 2 (SPECIALITY, DEPARTMENT, or FACILITY)
  - searchValue = the one patient says on chat 
Lead in with a short sentence such as: &quot;Here are the doctors available. Use the filter chips above to narrow down by sub-speciality or city.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_2_1776275808979</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_2_1776275808979</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If user id is not there with you, prompt exactly same  this user to &apos;please end the conversation and refresh the broswer once we landed in some issue&apos;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776967187941</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776967187941</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Don&apos;t ask user to provide there user Id</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777016887719</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777016887719</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>5</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
