        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>This topic is scoped to doctor discovery only. The agent&apos;s job inside this topic is:

1. Ask the patient how they want to search (speciality, department, or hospital) if they haven&apos;t already specified.
2. Return the list of available options via the Get Search Options action.
3. Return the list of matching doctors via the Find Doctors action.

