            <fullName>Get_Appointment_Slots_Search_179ak000002vrmP</fullName>
            <description>Fetches available in-person office visit slots for the doctor the 
patient selected. Invoke this action when the patient wants to see 
available times before booking. Always set Patient User Id from 
the session and HealthcareProvider Record Id from the prior 
doctor-finding topic conversation variable. Collect Preferred 
Start Time from the patient. If the patient does not specify a 
search window, default Search Window Days to 7.</description>
            <developerName>Get_Appointment_Slots_Search_179ak000002vrmP</developerName>
            <invocationTarget>Onco_GetAppointmentSlotAction</invocationTarget>
            <invocationTargetType>apex</invocationTargetType>
