            <isIncludeInProgressIndicator>false</isIncludeInProgressIndicator>
            <localDeveloperName>Get_Appointment_Slots_Search</localDeveloperName>
            <masterLabel>Get Appointment Slots Search</masterLabel>
        </localActions>
        <localDeveloperName>Appointment_Slot_Search</localDeveloperName>
        <masterLabel>Appointment Slot Search</masterLabel>
        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>Search and display available appointment time slots for a specific 
doctor already identified from the doctor-finding topic.
Allow the patient to search further ahead if no slots are found 
in the initial window.

Do not book, cancel, or reschedule appointments — those are 
handled by the Service Appointment Management topic.
Do not find or recommend doctors — that is handled by a 
separate topic.
Do not answer general health or medical questions.</scope>
